Localization.Name: Pulse "Piconalia" Laser Pistol
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Verified Offworld Laser Technologies
Item Type: Pistol
Class: Energy (Laser)

Battery Size: 60
Rate of Fire: 500 rpm (1000 rpm rapid)
Effective Range: 15m

Attachments: Optics (S1), Underbarrel (S1)

The Pulse Laser Pistol is a fully automatic pistol intended for close quarter combat. VOLT designed the weapon with a unique capacitor that condenses the pistol's laser energy, increasing its rate of fire at the cost of greater inaccuracy and a higher risk of overheating.

Light up the night this Luminalia with this green Piconalia edition.
